    </div>
  </div>
</section>

      <!-- Card 7: Multi-AI -->
      <div class="bento-card span-2">
        <div class="bento-num">05 · Orchestration</div>
        <div class="bento-title">ANY AI. ONE MEMORY.</div>
        <div class="bento-desc">Claude, GPT, Gemini, Perplexity, local LLMs — all connect via OAuth 2.0. Context transfers. Memory follows the conversation, not the vendor.</div>
        <div class="diagram">
