<!-- FEATURE DETAIL: MEMORY LOOP -->
<section class="feature-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-content">
        <div class="feature-num">03 · Memory</div>
        <h2 class="feature-title">THE MEMORY LOOP</h2>
        <p class="feature-desc">Conversational context becomes institutional knowledge. Three memory tiers — conversational, organizational, and personal — governed by humans and owned by your organization. Switch AI models and pick up exactly where you left off.</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Conversational memory: session-scoped, role-tagged</li>
          <li>Organizational memory: promoted, governed, immutable once approved</li>
          <li>Personal memory: behavioral patterns, preferences, decisions</li>
          <li>pgvector similarity search across all memory tiers</li>
          <li>Memory persists across AI model switches</li>
          <li>Dual-write synchronization: edge cache + fortress database</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-visual">
        <div class="visual-panel">
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.75rem">
